lead_paragraph: Jessica Thomas scored 21 points, Keyona Hayes had 18 and No. 18 Miami defeated Old Dominion 66-56 on Sunday for its seventh consecutive win.

headline.print_headline: Thomas, Hayes Lead No. 18 Miami Women by Old Dominion 66-56
